{"tid":1288334,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"八月尾去塔斯曼尼亞一問","createTime":"2019-07-05T14:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T18:47:38.000Z","uid":82119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4437fecc04d53021c2615840346ed5462b72d0e8","tid":1288334,"uid":82119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"八月尾打算打朋友去塔斯曼尼亞玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n但係好似正值嚴冬，想問下有無人呢段時間去過大約知幾凍到？其實最驚係冬天凍得劑啲景點刪哂門無嘢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋係咪一定要自駕遊先玩到？如果當地有無得靠public transport 去到景點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔識渣車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5b177d8e018a58e4ace400f1e552a21882c468","tid":1288334,"uid":123808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"可以試下join當地啲local tour"},{"pid":"fc94d9bbb69455625fac77daa624f6217c10c7f6","tid":1288334,"uid":82119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a5b177d8e018a58e4ace400f1e552a21882c468","tid":1288334,"uid":123808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"可以試下join當地啲local tour"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"有無推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89358a3e34666d0dd68329ab1357cccec9063f48","tid":1288334,"uid":82119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d2d75b1839472f9a069cf42f3f55ed412350d18","tid":1288334,"uid":82119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:34:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a19b24b840b6c5c5f8804647830d781536ce647","tid":1288334,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:55:37.000Z","msg":"上年9月份去，Hobart比Sydney要凍幾度到十幾度<br />\n8月去搖籃山有機會睇到雪"},{"pid":"fd944b618116e297836d1d657e0712155434b4c3","tid":1288334,"u